descriptionHTML:
Sleek, professional, and luxurious.

Golden Throne is an exquisite Watch Face for both business and pleasure.
A perfect balance between the classical and the modern.
Golden Throne designer Watch Face embodied force and style and revealed the unique personality.

- watch battery widget
- watch date of month widget
- watch widgets optional on / off
- supports round and squared watches



Customization of Golden Throne watch face

- Open Android Wear app
- Select Golden Throne elegant watch face in the selection
- One Click on the icon activates the watch face on your smart watch device
- Then Double click on icon brings you to customization page
- Now you can customize Golden Throne watch face ( date widget on /off and battery watch widget on / off )

It works on all Android Wear devices and supports round and square smartwatches.

Round ( Moto 360 and LG G watch R )
Square ( LG G watch and Samsung Gear Live , ASUS Zen Watch and Sony Smartwatch 3 )

Made in Germany - copyright© all rights reserved Maystarwerk
comments: Exquisite Bit expensive, but a lovely design. Looks good on my LG G (square face) would like to see more from this design house.
